"use strict";(self.webpackChunkwangdoc=self.webpackChunkwangdoc||[]).push([[7896],{80659:(e,a,s)=>{s.r(a),s.d(a,{data:()=>n});const n={key:"v-aefcf406",path:"/git-tutorial/commands/git-commit.html",title:"git commit",lang:"zh-CN",frontmatter:{summary:"git commit git commit命令用于将暂存区中的变化提交到仓库区。 -m参数用于指定 commit 信息，是必需的。如果省略-m参数，git commit会自动打开文本编辑器，要求输入。 git commit命令可以跳过暂存区，直接将文件从工作区提交到仓库区。 上面命令会将工作区中指定文件的变化，先添加到暂存区，然后再将暂存区提交到仓库区。 命",head:[["meta",{property:"og:url",content:"https://yzqbooks.github.io/wangdoc/wangdoc/git-tutorial/commands/git-commit.html"}],["meta",{property:"og:site_name",content:"wangdoc"}],["meta",{property:"og:title",content:"git commit"}],["meta",{property:"og:type",content:"article"}],["meta",{property:"og:updated_time",content:"2022-04-06T10:09:00.000Z"}],["meta",{property:"og:locale",content:"zh-CN"}],["meta",{property:"article:modified_time",content:"2022-04-06T10:09:00.000Z"}]]},excerpt:"",headers:[{level:2,title:"命令行参数",slug:"命令行参数",children:[{level:3,title:"-a",slug:"a",children:[]},{level:3,title:"--allow-empty",slug:"allow-empty",children:[]},{level:3,title:"--amend",slug:"amend",children:[]},{level:3,title:"--fixup",slug:"fixup",children:[]},{level:3,title:"-m",slug:"m",children:[]},{level:3,title:"--squash",slug:"squash",children:[]}]}],git:{createdTime:164923974e4,updatedTime:164923974e4,contributors:[{name:"yzqdev",email:"yzqdev@outlook.com",commits:1}]},readingTime:{minutes:1.5,words:449},filePathRelative:"git-tutorial/commands/git-commit.md"}},91833:(e,a,s)=>{s.r(a),s.d(a,{default:()=>i});const n=(0,s(66252).uE)('<h1 id="git-commit" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#git-commit" aria-hidden="true">#</a> git commit</h1><p><code>git commit</code>命令用于将暂存区中的变化提交到仓库区。</p><p><code>-m</code>参数用于指定 commit 信息，是必需的。如果省略<code>-m</code>参数，<code>git commit</code>会自动打开文本编辑器，要求输入。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> commit -m <span class="token string">&quot;message&quot;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p><code>git commit</code>命令可以跳过暂存区，直接将文件从工作区提交到仓库区。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> commit <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>filename<span class="token operator">&gt;</span>  -m <span class="token string">&quot;message&quot;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>上面命令会将工作区中指定文件的变化，先添加到暂存区，然后再将暂存区提交到仓库区。</p><h2 id="命令行参数" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#命令行参数" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 命令行参数</h2><h3 id="a" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#a" aria-hidden="true">#</a> -a</h3><p><code>-a</code>参数用于先将所有工作区的变动文件，提交到暂存区，再运行<code>git commit</code>。用了<code>-a</code>参数，就不用执行<code>git add .</code>命令了。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> commit -am <span class="token string">&quot;message&quot;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>如果没有指定提交说明，运行下面的命令会直接打开默认的文本编辑器，让用户撰写提交说明。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> commit -a\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><h3 id="allow-empty" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#allow-empty" aria-hidden="true">#</a> --allow-empty</h3><p><code>--allow-empty</code>参数用于没有提交信息的 commit。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> commit --allow-empty\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><h3 id="amend" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#amend" aria-hidden="true">#</a> --amend</h3><p><code>--amend</code>参数用于撤销上一次 commit，然后生成一个新的 commit。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> commit --amend - m <span class="token string">&quot;new commit message&quot;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><h3 id="fixup" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#fixup" aria-hidden="true">#</a> --fixup</h3><p><code>--fixup</code>参数的含义是，当前添加的 commit 是以前某一个 commit 的修正。以后执行互动式的<code>git rebase</code>的时候，这两个 commit 将会合并成一个。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> commit --fixup <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>commit<span class="token operator">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>执行上面的命令，提交说明将自动生成，即在目标 commit 的提交说明的最前面，添加“fixup! ”这个词。</p><h3 id="m" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#m" aria-hidden="true">#</a> -m</h3><p><code>-m</code>参数用于添加提交说明。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> commit -m <span class="token string">&quot;message&quot;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><h3 id="squash" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#squash" aria-hidden="true">#</a> --squash</h3><p><code>--squash</code>参数的作用与<code>--fixup</code>类似，表示当前添加的 commit 应该与以前某一个 commit 合并成一个，以后执行互动式的<code>git rebase</code>的时候，这两个 commit 将会合并成一个。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> commit --squash <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>commit<span class="token operator">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div>',29),t={},i=(0,s(83744).Z)(t,[["render",function(e,a){return n}]])},83744:(e,a)=>{a.Z=(e,a)=>{const s=e.__vccOpts||e;for(const[e,n]of a)s[e]=n;return s}}}]);